      "rationale": "CAD geometry verified against CMM measurements of the physical test article (max deviation 0.03 mm). Rotational speed set to tachometer-measured values ±0.5 RPM. Fluid properties matched to measured values. Equivalency established for adult validation conditions. For pediatric operating points, the same geometry and fluid properties apply; rotational speed targets for pediatric flow delivery have been specified in the device IFU but were not independently verified in a test configuration at those speeds."
